originalSql:
SELECT 
    p.Id AS PostId,
    p.Title,
    p.CreationDate AS PostCreationDate,
    p.Score,
    p.ViewCount,
    COALESCE(a.AcceptedAnswerCount, 0) AS AcceptedAnswerCount,
    COALESCE(c.CommentCount, 0) AS CommentCount,
    COALESCE(v.VoteCount, 0) AS VoteCount,
    u.Reputation AS UserReputation,
    u.Location AS UserLocation,
    u.CreationDate AS UserCreationDate
FROM 
    Posts p
LEFT JOIN 
    (SELECT 
         ParentId, 
         COUNT(*) AS AcceptedAnswerCount 
     FROM Posts 
     WHERE PostTypeId = 2 AND AcceptedAnswerId IS NOT NULL 
     GROUP BY ParentId) a ON p.Id = a.ParentId
LEFT JOIN 
    (SELECT 
         PostId, 
         COUNT(*) AS CommentCount 
     FROM Comments 
     GROUP BY PostId) c ON p.Id = c.PostId
LEFT JOIN 
    (SELECT 
         PostId, 
         COUNT(*) AS VoteCount 
     FROM Votes 
     GROUP BY PostId) v ON p.Id = v.PostId
JOIN 
    Users u ON p.OwnerUserId = u.Id
WHERE 
    p.CreationDate >= '2023-01-01' 
ORDER BY 
    p.CreationDate DESC 
LIMIT 100

SELECT COALESCE("Id", "Id") AS "Id", "Reputation", "CreationDate", "DisplayName", "LastAccessDate", "WebsiteUrl", "Location", "AboutMe", "Views", "UpVotes", "DownVotes", "ProfileImageUrl", "AccountId"
FROM "Users"

SELECT COALESCE("Posts"."Id", "Posts"."Id") AS "POSTID", "Posts"."Title" AS "TITLE", "Posts"."CreationDate" AS "POSTCREATIONDATE", "Posts"."Score" AS "SCORE", "Posts"."ViewCount" AS "VIEWCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t2"."ACCEPTEDANSWERCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t2"."ACCEPTEDANSWERCOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "ACCEPTEDANSWERCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t4"."COMMENTCOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t4"."COMMENTCOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "COMMENTCOUNT", CASE WHEN "t6"."VOTECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t6"."VOTECOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "VOTECOUNT", "s1"."Reputation" AS "USERREPUTATION", "s1"."Location" AS "USERLOCATION", "s1"."CreationDate" AS "USERCREATIONDATE"
FROM "Posts"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "ParentId" AS "PARENTID", COUNT(*) AS "ACCEPTEDANSWERCOUNT"
FROM "Posts"
WHERE CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2
GROUP BY "ParentId") AS "t2" ON "Posts"."Id" = "t2"."PARENTID"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "PostId" AS "POSTID", COUNT(*) AS "COMMENTCOUNT"
FROM "Comments"
GROUP BY "PostId") AS "t4" ON "Posts"."Id" = "t4"."POSTID"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "PostId" AS "POSTID", COUNT(*) AS "VOTECOUNT"
FROM "Votes"
GROUP BY "PostId") AS "t6" ON "Posts"."Id" = "t6"."POSTID"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "Posts"."OwnerUserId" = "s1"."Id"
WHERE "Posts"."CreationDate" >= '2023-01-01'
ORDER BY "Posts"."CreationDate" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 100
